  "title": "Sales Executive (Legal Firm)",
  "description": "<p>📍 Location: Central Singapore <br />💰 Salary: Up to $3,000 (Basic) + Comms  <br />🕒 Work Week: 5 days<br />Working Hours: Mon - Fri (10am-6pm), Alternate Saturdays (10am-6pm) off day will be replaced on Wednesdays</p><p><br /></p><p>Our client is a Singapore-based legal services firm specializing in estate planning and corporate governance. They offer comprehensive legal solutions, including the drafting of wills and Lasting Powers of Attorney (LPAs).</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Following up with ready leads and service existing clients on estate planning services.</li><li>Understanding client's needs, explaning the importance of wills and LPAs.</li><li>Providing advice on the benefits of having these documents in place.</li><li>Assisting clients with gathering information and completing necessary forms for drafting wills and LPAs.</li><li>Establishing strong relationships with clients to ensure their satisfaction and encourage repeat business.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min GCE 'O' Levels.</li><li><strong>No experience needed - Training provided.</strong></li><li>Pleasant personality and good interpersonal skills.</li></ul><p></p><p>To apply, kindly click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> to submit your latest CV</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>SAAY</strong></p><p>EA Registration No.: R25139436</p><p>EA License No.: 25C2695</p>",
